text: Han River Police () is a 2023 South Korean action comedy television series written and directed by Kim Sang-cheol, starring Kwon Sang-woo, Kim Hee-won, Lee Sang-yi, Bae Da-bin and Shin Hyun-seung. It aired on Disney+ from September 13 to September 27, 2023. == Cast == Source: == Production == === Development === The series was announced on Disney+ consisting of six episodes. The press conference was held at the JW Marriott Dongdaemun in Jongno-gu, Seoul on September 12, 2023. === Casting === Kwon Sang-woo, Kim Hee-won, Lee Sang-yi and Bae Da-bin along with Shin Hyun-seung were reportedly cast to appear. === Filming === Principal photography began on August 15, 2022 and filming was wrapped up on January 5, 2023. == Release == The series was made available to stream on Disney+ on September 13 2023. == Reception == Carmen Chin of NME awarded the series two stars out of five. Melissa Foong of Lifestyle Asia and Stephen McCarty of South China Morning Post reviewed the series. == References == == Other websites == * * Category:2023 television series debuts Category:2023 television series endings
